OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775995869
OL,3,CSix men jailed for violent burglary
OL,4,Cwhich left two people seriously injured
OL,6,FSix men have been sentenced to nearly
OL,7,F70 years' in jail following a violent
OL,8,Fburglary near Maidstone that left two
OL,9,Fpeople with serious injuries.
OL,11,FAt around 8.10pm on 23 December 2024,
OL,12,Ffive men forced entry into a home near
OL,13,FHeath Road.
OL,15,FArmed with a knife and a crowbar, the
OL,16,Fgroup assaulted two men inside the
OL,17,Fproperty before stealing a watch and
OL,18,Ffleeing the scene in two cars.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
