OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775995869
OL,3,CSix men jailed for violent burglary
OL,4,Cwhich left two people seriously injured
OL,6,FOfficers attended alongside
OL,7,Fparamedics, with both men - who are in
OL,8,Ftheir 40s - taken to hospital
OL,9,Fsuffering serious head injuries.
OL,11,FOne of the two also sustained
OL,12,Fsignificant wounds to his arm and hand.
OL,14,FThe weapons used in the attack were
OL,15,Frecovered at the scene, and detectives
OL,16,Fimmediately launched a complex and
OL,17,Ffast moving investigation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
