OL,3,CSix men jailed for violent burglary
OL,4,Cwhich left two people seriously injured
OL,6,FBetween 31 December 2024 and 3 March
OL,7,F2025, Kent Police arrested and charged
OL,8,Fthe suspects having uncovered a wealth
OL,9,Fof compelling evidence, including:
OL,11,FFive of the men denied their
OL,12,Finvolvement but were convicted
OL,13,Ffollowing a trial and sentenced at
OL,14,FMaidstone Crown Court on Thursday 2
OL,15,FApril:
OL,17,FTyresse Johnson, 23, of Challenger
OL,18,FClose, Rainham, pleaded guilty and was
OL,19,Fsentenced to nine years' imprisonment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
