PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775995869
OL,3,CSix men jailed for violent burglary
OL,4,Cwhich left two people seriously injured
OL,6,FInvestigating officer, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Joshua Littley, said "The
OL,8,Flengthy custodial sentences handed
OL,9,Fdown reflect the astonishing and
OL,10,Fsustained level of violence involved
OL,11,Fin this offence.
OL,13,FThe victims not only suffered serious
OL,14,Fphysical injuries but were left deeply
OL,15,Ftraumatised by the attack.
OL,17,FKent Police officers worked tirelessly
OL,18,Fto identify those responsible,
OL,19,Fmeticulously gathering evidence that
OL,20,Fleft the offenders with nowhere to
OL,21,Fhide.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
