OL,3,CSix men jailed for violent burglary
OL,4,Cwhich left two people seriously injured
OL,6,FI welcome these sentences and hope
OL,7,Fthey offer reassurance to the victims
OL,8,Fand the public that those responsible
OL,9,Fare now behind bars and unable to
OL,10,Fcause further harm."
